PropertyValue.String: Reads withholding tax data of supplier invoice.
Reads the withholding tax data of the supplier invoice using, for example, the supplier invoice, the fiscal year, and the document currency.
Reads withholding tax data of supplier invoice by key data.
Reads withholding tax data of supplier invoice using the key fields for document number, fiscal year, and withholding tax type.
Reads account assignment data of supplier invoice item.
Reads the account assignment data of the supplier invoice item using, for example, the supplier invoice, the ordinal number and the supplier invoice item.
Reads account assignment data of supplier invoice item by key data.
Reads account assignment data of supplier invoice item using the key fields for document number, fiscal year, supplier invoice item and, ordinal number
Reads supplier invoice item data with purchase order reference.

Reads the data of the supplier invoice item with purchase order reference using, for example, the supplier invoice, the fiscal year, the plant, the document currency, the purchase order, the amount of the supplier invoice item, and the tax code.
Reads supplier invoice item data with purchase order reference by key data.
Reads supplier invoice item data with purchase order reference using key fields or document number, fiscal year, and supplier invoice item.
Reads supplier invoice data.

Reads the supplier invoice data using, for example, the supplier invoice, the fiscal year, the company code, the document currency, the document date, the invoice gross amount, the invoicing party and the posting date.
Reads supplier invoice data by key data.
Reads supplier invoice data by key fields for document number and fiscal year.
Reads supplier invoice item data for posting to G/L account.

Reads the data of the supplier invoice item for posting to G/L account using, for example, the supplier invoice, the fiscal year, the document currency, the debit credit code, and the amount of the supplier invoice.
Reads supplier invoice item data for posting to G/L account by key data.
Reads the supplier invoice item data for posting to G/L account by key fields for document number, fiscal year, and supplier invoice item.
Reads supplier invoice item data for posting to asset.

Reads the data of the supplier invoice item for posting to asset using, for example, the supplier invoice, the fiscal year, the document currency, the debit credit code, and the amount of the supplier invoice.
Reads supplier invoice item data for posting to asset by key data.
Reads the supplier invoice item data for posting to asset by key fields for document number, fiscal year, and supplier invoice item.
Reads supplier invoice item data for posting to material.

Reads the data of the supplier invoice item for posting to material using, for example, the supplier invoice, the fiscal year, the document currency, the debit credit code, and the amount of the supplier invoice.
Reads supplier invoice item data for posting to material by key data.
Reads the supplier invoice item data for posting to material by key fields for document number, fiscal year, and supplier invoice item.
Reads tax data for supplier invoice.
Reads the tax data of the supplier invoice using, for example, the supplier invoice, the fiscal year, the tax counter in the supplier invoice, the tax code, and the document currency.
Reads tax data for supplier invoice by key data.
Reads tax data for supplier invoice by key fields for document number, fiscal year, tax code, and supplier invoice tax counter.
Reads additional data for supplier invoice.
Reads the additional data of the supplier invoice using, for example, the supplier invoice, the fiscal year, the supplier name , the supplier bank details, and the one-time account details.
Reads additional data for supplier invoice by key data.
Reads additional data for supplier invoice by key fields for document number, fiscal year, supplier, supplier bank data, and one-time account data.
Reads entered delivery note data for supplier invoice.
Reads the entered delivery note data of the supplier invoice using, for example, the supplier invoice, the fiscal year, and the inbound delivery note.
Reads entered delivery note data for supplier invoice by key data.
Reads entered delivery note data for supplier invoice by key fields for document number, fiscal year, and inbound delivery note.
Reads entered service entry sheet (Lean) data for supplier invoice.
Reads the entered service entry sheet (Lean) data of the supplier invoice using, for example, the supplier invoice, the fiscal year, the service entry sheet, and the service entry sheet item.
Reads entered service entry sheet (Lean) data for supplier invoice by key data.
Reads entered service entry sheet (Lean) data for supplier invoice by key fields for document number, fiscal year, service entry sheet, and service entry sheet item.
Reads entered purchasing document data for supplier invoice.
Reads the entered purchasing document data of the supplier invoice using, for example, the supplier invoice, the fiscal year, the purchase order, and the purchase order item.
Reads entered purchasing document data for supplier invoice by key data.
Reads entered purchasing document data for supplier invoice by key fields for document number, fiscal year, purchase order, and purchase order item.
Creates a supplier invoice.

Creates a supplier invoice using, for example, the company code, the invoice gross amount, and the invoicing party. The service supports a deep create of an invoice. In addition, you can park or hold an invoice with header data only.
Deletes supplier invoice that has not been posted.
Deletes not-posted supplier invoice (for example in status Held or Parked) using the supplier invoice and the fiscal year.

Annotation.String: Reverses a supplier invoice and returns the reversal number.
Reverses a supplier invoice and creates a reversal document. The system returns the reversal number.

PropertyValue.String: Reads the item data with purchase order reference including the account assignment data.
Reads the data of an item with purchase order reference and the corresponding account assignment data.
Reads the supplier invoice data and the item data with purchase order reference.
Reads the header data of the supplier invoice and the data of items with purchase order reference.
Reads the supplier invoice data and the item data for posting to G/L account.
Reads the header data of the supplier invoice and the data of items for posting to G/L account.
Reads the supplier invoice data and the item data for posting to asset.
Reads the header data of the supplier invoice and the data of items for posting to asset.
Reads the supplier invoice data and the item data for posting to material.
Reads the header data of the supplier invoice and the data of items for posting to material.
Reads the supplier invoice data including the tax data.
Reads the header data of the supplier invoice including the tax data.
Reads the supplier invoice data including the withholding tax data.
Reads the header data of the supplier invoice including the withholding tax data.
Reads the supplier invoice data including the additional data.
Reads the header data of the supplier invoice including the additional data.
Reads the supplier invoice data including the entered delivery note data.
Reads the header data of the supplier invoice including the entered delivery note data.
Reads the supplier invoice data including the entered service entry sheet (Lean) data.
Reads the header data of the supplier invoice including the entered service entry sheet (Lean) data.
Reads the supplier invoice data including the entered purchasing document data.
Reads the header data of the supplier invoice including the entered purchasing document data.
